window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After finding out the traumatic truth, Keira tries to move on from the doors of Afterlife and the love lost through a world of pain. But Afterlife's King isn't yet done with her, and Keira once again finds herself stood opposite the man who broke her heart. </p><p>However, the truth that she thought she knew will soon unravel, and Keira finds herself following the ribbon of lies all the way to the very gates of hell. And as Keira knows more than most, the pursuit of truth can be a dangerous game to play when your opponents are supernatural killers. But can everyone be trusted? </p><p>Please note that the book is written using UK English spelling, with some local Northern sayings and descriptions. </p>"; 
